cli/README.md
     1тЖТ# Command-line tool
     2тЖТ
     3тЖТThe `mdbook` command-line tool is used to create and build books.
     4тЖТAfter you have [installed](../guide/installation.md) `mdbook`, you can run the `mdbook help` command in your terminal to view the available commands.
     5тЖТ
     6тЖТThis following sections provide in-depth information on the different commands available.
     7тЖТ
     8тЖТ* [`mdbook init <directory>`](init.md) --- Creates a new book with minimal boilerplate to start with.
     9тЖТ* [`mdbook build`](build.md) --- Renders the book.
